content:
Posted: August 26, 2016
Product received for free
												As a HUGE Sonic nerd myself, I have to say, this is one of the best Sonic games yet! The graphics and gameplay are really smooth, and Sonic is actually pretty fast in this game, unlike in some others... (cough) Sonic Lost World (cough)There are some pretty awesome scenes throughout out the games, too, like escaping from the Mega Chopper. This game is just amazingly detailed and really has a vibe that not many other Sonic games have brought before. I definitely recommend this game to someone who's new to the Sonic franchise.P.S, Time Eater's hard ;~;
